   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The system has minimum clearances requirements from the top <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b> and from the back <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b>, for airflow and to be able
to transport the system.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">It is possible to place systems side by side. It is recommended
to not have any direct contact between the side walls.</p>
      <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">Always make sure that there is enough space
for the warm air to dissipate.</note>
